snippet.title: Crayta Announcement Trailer – Play A Different Game
snippet.description:
Crayta is a collaborative game creation, sharing, and play platform, coming exclusively to Stadia, Summer 2020. It brings together people of all ages, experience, ability and background to create multiplayer games. All trailer footage was captured within Crayta.

Find out how we created our trailer entirely within the game in this stream: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A0ugXWKY1KM&list=PLJHJuuXh6_dJ28baBPvr-gbN5xkeNUPFz&index=5&t=2758s

Stay up to date by following us:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CraytaGame
Discord: http://discord.gg/crayta
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/Crayta
Medium: https://medium.com/crayta
Play now: https://www.crayta.com/

#Crayta #Stadia
